Academic Student Employees (BX)
UC Mini-Package A
August 16, 2022

UC MINI-PACKAGE A

The elements of this proposal are offered as a mini-package, whereby acceptance of all components is
necessary for a tentative agreement on the package as a whole. Absent such agreement, both Parties are
allowed to revert to the status quo ante on all matters covered by this proposal.
• Article 29 - Union Security – UC Proposal 3 - August 16, 2022
• Article 12 - Grievance and Arbitration – UC Proposal 5 - August 16, 2022
• Article 2 – Appointment Notification – UC Proposal 3 – June 10, 2022
• Article 25 – Summer Session – UC Proposal 1 – July 12, 2022
• Article 28 – Union Access and Rights – UC Proposal 3 - July 12, 2022
